item.title: CVE-2021-27389|2024-08-03T20:48:16.625Z -- siemens -- opcenter%20quality
item.description: A vulnerability has been identified in Opcenter Quality (All versions < V12.2), QMS Automotive (All versions < V12.30). A private sign key is shipped with the product without adequate protection.
